  - 'log a 1-hour walk'
  - 'I did yoga for 20 minutes'

Convert duration to MINUTES. The activity_type is freeform — pass the user's
phrase verbatim ('running', 'cycling', 'yoga', 'crossfit', 'walk', 'swim').
